-- Imperial County EMS Agency protocols
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'IMP-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'Imperial County EMS cardiac arrest protocol. High-quality CPR. Defibrillation for shockable rhythms. Epinephrine 1mg IV/IO q3-5min. Amiodarone for refractory VF/pVT.', 'https://www.icphd.org/environmental-health/emergency-medical-services/', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Imperial County EMS Agency' AND c.state = 'California';
